doc.previous: Electras were popular as private planes for royalty in Asia and Europe In India the Maharaja of Jammu Kashmir and the Maharaja of Jodhpur both purchased them for their personal use in 1937 6
doc.after: The Electra was produced in several variants for both civilian and military customers Lockheed built a total of 149 Electras
